## Kyiv Metro

For the metropolitan area surrounding the city of [Kyiv](/Kyiv), see [Kyiv metropolitan area](/Kyiv_metropolitan_area).

### Overview

**Native name:**
*   Київський метрополітен
*   Kyivs'kyi metropoliten

**Owner:** [Kyiv City Council](/Kyiv_City_Council)
**Locale:** [Kyiv](/Kyiv)
**Transit type:** [Rapid transit](/Rapid_transit)
**Number of lines:** 3 &#91;1&#93;&#160;&#91;2&#93;
**Number of stations:** 52 (2 under construction)
**Daily ridership:** 1.32 million (2016) &#91;2&#93;
**Annual ridership:** 484.56 million (2016) &#91;2&#93;
**Website:** metro.kyiv.ua

### Operation

**Began operation:** 6 November 1960 (65 years ago) (1960-11-06)
**Operator(s):** Kyivs'kyi Metropoliten
**Number of vehicles:** 824 cars &#91;2&#93; (in 130 trains)

